                        "type": "0",
                        "version": 0,
                        "content": "The nurse is preparing to administer a dose of naloxone intravenously to a client with an opioid overdose. Which supportive medical equipment would the nurse plan to have at the client's bedside if needed?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "80db17ea97ed8fdcd1b6b9666390fca1",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Applying 应用",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nThe nurse administering naloxone for suspected opioid overdose would have resuscitation equipment readily available to support naloxone therapy if it is needed. Other adjuncts that may be needed include oxygen, a mechanical ventilator, and vasopressors.",
                        "id": "0b774809338845a783d456f172a75e1e",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "98e9ab3452cc4d2da1563c2921da719d",
                                "content": "Place the head of the bed flat."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "3ad2c05cb780450ba4ff7851447b98e6",
                                "content": "Ensure that naloxone is readily available."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "25f498ddff344dd29c2904ecc3d9b8c5",
                                "content": "Flush the catheter with 6 mL of sterile water."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "da21d40fbb4940d18fa171b8855fd8f1",
                                "content": "Aspirate with a syringe to ensure a cerebrospinal fluid (CSF) return."
                            }
                        ],
                        "extJson": {
                            "optionList": [
                                {
                                    "isRight": "0",
                                    "userAnswer": "",
                                    "isSelected": "0",
                                    "id": "98e9ab3452cc4d2da1563c2921da719d",
                                    "content": "Place the head of the bed flat."
                                },
                                {
                                    "isRight": "1",
                                    "userAnswer": "",
                                    "isSelected": "0",
                                    "id": "3ad2c05cb780450ba4ff7851447b98e6",
                                    "content": "Ensure that naloxone is readily available."
                                },
                                {
                                    "isRight": "0",
                                    "userAnswer": "",
                                    "isSelected": "0",
                                    "id": "25f498ddff344dd29c2904ecc3d9b8c5",
                                    "content": "Flush the catheter with 6 mL of sterile water."
                                },
                                {
                                    "isRight": "0",
                                    "userAnswer": "",
                                    "isSelected": "0",
                                    "id": "da21d40fbb4940d18fa171b8855fd8f1",
